<L>__{interior club. night}
<A>__{danny and david are at the bar, having just finished talking to rachman. danny puffs out his cheeks and shakes his head.}
<C>__{danny}
<D>__{well, i'm not sure you'd want him to marry your sister. i'm not even sure you'd want to talk to him in a night club, come to that.}
<A>__{they both chuckle. there is a silence for a moment.}
<C>__{danny}
<P>__{(gently)}
<D>__{you do know what you're doing, old chap? with jenny?}
<C>__{david}
<D>__{this is the one, danny.}
<C>__{danny}
<D>__{we've heard that before.}
<C>__{david}
<D>__{you can see she's different. she's got everything. you've got helen, and....}
<C>__{danny}
<P>__{(drily)}
<D>__{and you've got helen with brains.}
<C>__{david}
<P>__{(rumbled)}
<D>__{yes.}
<C>__{danny}
<D>__{i don't want to see her hurt.}
<A>__{they make their way back to their table.}
